parameters:
Former Mayor: Hey, youngster... That was quite the fight
earlier... To think you could still move like that after
battling me.

Shark Broccoli: Mayor... I'm sorry... I wasn't myself... To
think I tried to defeat you, stage a coup, and seize control
of the city...

Former Mayor: Having spirit is good, isn't it! I may no
longer be the mayor, but I can't let that orca bastard do as
he pleases.

Former Mayor: If we can't do it openly, we'll do it from the
shadows... Maybe it's time to start an underground
organization! I'll take that warehouse costume as
compensation.

Brachiocondor: Gugugu... From today on, I am the monster
"Brachiocondor"!! It's a contest between you and me to see
who can build a huge organization and eventually defeat that
orca jerk and take back Mudachi City!

Brachiocondor: ...It's getting kind of hot... Maybe I should
take off this monster suit...

Memimi: Oh, surprisingly... You're slimmer than I thought,
Brachiocondor...

Brachiocondor: Both Shark Broccoli and I are betting on you.
Do your best!
